已解决,[删除方案](https://doris.apache.org/zh-CN/docs/dev/sql-manual/sql-reference/Data-Manipulation-Statements/Manipulation/DELETE?_highlight=delete_without_partition#description)
1 执行时设置 SET delete_without_partition=TRUE
2 执行语句：DELETE FROM test_table PARTITION p20220820 WHERE day_id=20220820
3 执行删除时 添加指定分区名称(PARTITION p20220820)即可
Understand, thank you
